# Directions to L50 Cleric GM (Iris, mob 11001)

say { "hello";
	smile %n;
	say Hello %n, what can I do for you?;
	}
        
say { "next guildmaster";
	tell %n Finding your next guildmaster is part of your training.;
	tell %n However, I can give you a hint...;
	tell %n Seek the beautiful bride of Desade.;
	tell %n Any well known adventurer would indeed be found,;
	tell %n With his head slightly above the ground.;
	tell %n Though if you lack in strength,;
	tell %n Its heavenly gates you will not take.;
	}

